Localization.Name: Aloprat Skewer
Localization.Description:
NDR: 25
Effects: Immune Suppressing

Aloprat is a hearty species of rodent found across Human occupied space, and even can survive aboard space stations and ships eating a variety of food and scraps. This aloprat has been skewered and roasted rotisserie style for crisp skin and gamey, fatty meat.
